public class ExecutionComposite
extends org.eclipse.swt.widgets.Composite

The composite for the ExecutionWindow. It offers most of its element and the corresponding methods. It heavily utilizes the supplied ExecutionRunner instance.

Version:
1.0.0, 2010-08-28
Author:

executionFinished

protected void executionFinished()
Set that the execution is finished. This will disable the pause / resume Button, make the abort Button act as an exit button and set the field isFinished to true. If the window is minimized, the try item's tooltip will be updated.
